title.narrative: Partnership for Regional East Africa Counterterror. Other Costs - Ferensic Advisor PR4200462 thrue. Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services - Other U.S. Government Agency Contract Services (A, B, C) (ITA). SGG80015V0477 INL-Materials/Books for general Lead

description.narrative: This award strives to help foreign partners professionalize their military forces through educational programs and technical support, ensuring that their force can develop and maintain the requisite capacity to effectively carry out its military mission through reliance on discipline, accountability, effective professional standards, and technical expertise. More specifically, this includes Daniel J. Epstein, Desk Officer (COR)[Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.]. SUPPLY/TRANSP/PROCUREMENT Daniel J. Epstein, Desk Officer (COR)[Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.]. Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.. SUPPLY/TRANSP/PROCUREMENT[Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.]. TRAFFICKING IN PERSONS[Covers services supplied by other U.S. Government agencies not otherwise classified.].

Through educational programs and technical support, help foreign partners professionalize their military forces, ensuring that their force can develop and maintain the requisite capacity to effectively carry out its military mission through reliance on discipline, accountability, effective professional standards, and technical expertise. In addition, activities assist foreign partners so that their military forces reliably demonstrate consistent support for adherence to norms of human rights; support the concept of civilian executive authority/control of the military; and have the capacity for institutional and security sector reform.
